<br>
1.Tash/Charm/Haste pet<br>
2.Tash Mob, Root Mob.. Sick pet on mob then slow..<br>
3. Sit on horse till mob is down to 2 bubs, then nuke..<br>
4. Run out find another mob or 2..<br>
5. Tash/Mez/Slow yer next mobs<br>
6. Sick pet on next mob rinse and repet.<br>
<br>
Side Note: If you happen to find a pet that seems to hold the charm well, and want to keep it. Invis, to break the charm when pet is low on life. Mez yer pet. Mem blur yer pet, which will Complete Heal him. Then re-tash, med for a lil bit and recharm.. And off you go again.<br>
<br>
Works same in PoD/PoI.. (just not the running room in PoI)<br>
<br>
/shrug That's what got me 2 lvls and 29 AA's in a little under 2 months..<br>
<br>
